<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ج<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>... وَخَدَتْ بِهِمْ هِمَمٌ لَهُمْ وَعَزَائِمُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>نَحْوَ الْمَنَازِلَ أَوَّلَ الأَزْمَانِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>رُفِعَتْ لَهُمْ فِي السَّيْرِ أَعْلامُ الْوِصَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>لِ فَشَمِّرُوا يَا خَيْبَةَ الْكَسْلانِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَرَأَوا عَلَى بُعْدٍ خِيَامًا مُشْرِفَا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>تٍ مُشْرِقَاتِ النُّورِ وَالْبُرْهَانِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَتَيَمَّمُوا تِلْكَ الْخِيَامَ فَآنَسُوا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>فِيهِنَّ أَقْمَارًا بِلا نُقْصَانِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>مِنْ قَاصِرَاتِ الطَّرْفِ لا تَبْغِي سِوَى<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>مَحْبُوبِهَا مِنْ سَائِرِ الشُّبَّانِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>قَصَرَتْ عَلَيْهِ طَرْفَهَا مِنْ حُسْنِهِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَالطَّرْفُ فِي ذَا الْوَجْهِ لِلنَّسْوَانِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>أَوْ أَنَّهَا قَصَرَتْ عَلَيْهِ طَرْفَهُ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>مِنْ حُسْنِهَا فَالطَّرْفُ لِلذُّكْرَانِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَالأَوَّلُ الْمَعْهُودُ مِنْ وَضْعِ الْخِطَا<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>بِ فَلا تَحُدْ عَنْ ظَاهِرِ الْقُرْآنِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَلَرُبَّمَا دَلَّتْ إِشَارَتُه عَلَى الثَّـ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>ـانِي فَتِلْكَ إِشَارَةٌ لِمَعَانِي<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>هَذَا وَلَيْسَ الْقَاصِرَاتُ كَمَنْ غَدَتْ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>مَقْصُورَةً فَهُمَا إِذًا صِنْفَانِ ... &gt;?<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>